Rental Qualifications and Policies for this property:<br>
• FICO score of 695 or higher<br>
• Income of three times the rent<br>
• No evictions nor open bankruptcies<br>
• Owner will not accept a cosigner<br>
• Security deposit must be received within 24 hours of approved application unless other arrangements are made in advance<br>
• Must take possession of the property within two weeks of approved application<br>
• One dog under 30lbs or one cat with breed restrictions and additional deposit<br>
• No smoking of any kind is allowed in the home<br>
• Owner pays $50 towards water with tenant paying the remainder. Owner pays for sewer and trash<br>
• Available with a ten-month lease term<br>
<br>
Near Madison Avenue and Dewey Drive in Larchmont Hills, Fair Oaks, this immaculate, corner lot, two-story, single family home offers four bedrooms, two full bathrooms and one half bathroom. This home has programmable central heat and air conditioning. The seven panel, oak and leaded glass door features sidelights with etched glass. The tile entry opens onto new laminate flooring, new paint, overhead lighting, dual pane windows with new two-inch blinds and verticals throughout 1,744 square feet of living space. The living room has laminate flooring and a floor to ceiling brick hearth and gas fireplace. The dining room has laminate flooring, chandelier and a door to the kitchen. The family room has tile flooring, overhead lighting, stairs to the second floor, access to the half bathroom, door to the garage and a slider to the rear yard.<br>
<br>
The eat-in kitchen has tile flooring, pendant lighting, wood cabinets, tile counters, pantry and is equipped with:<br>
• New, frost-free, stainless steel refrigerator<br>
• New, electric, stainless steel, glass-top range with self-cleaning oven<br>
• New, stainless steel dishwasher<br>
• Double sink with convertible faucet and garbage disposal<br>
<br>
The bedrooms and remaining bathrooms are located upstairs. The master bedroom has laminate flooring, overhead lighting and a double-door closet. The master bathroom has laminate and tile flooring, glass and tile walk-in shower with safety bar, marble and oak vanity and a double door closet. The second bedroom has laminate flooring and a four-door closet. The hall bathroom has tile flooring, tile shower over tub, marble and oak vanity and an etched glass window. The third and fourth bedrooms have laminate flooring and two-door closets.<br>
<br>
The fenced, beautifully landscaped rear yard has a partially covered patio, an uncovered brick patio, fruit tree and is equipped with automatic sprinklers in front and rear. Yard maintenance for the front and rear yards is tenant responsibility. In the two-car garage there is a workbench, lots of cabinets, overhead shelf, ramp into the house, gas water heater and a laundry area with electric dryer hookup and is equipped with new washer and dryer. This home is located in the San Juan Unified School District a few blocks from Del Campo High School.<br>
<br>
• Yard maintenance is tenant responsibility.<br>
<br>
Our applications are run one at a time, starting with the first completed application received. You may wish to apply immediately if you think you want to rent this property. We strongly encourage you to view the property prior to completing an application. Security deposit must be received within 24 hours of approved application unless other arrangements are made in advance. You must take possession of the property within two weeks of your approved application. If you have any questions or would like to make sure you meet the minimum criteria for this property, please call prior to applying. We respond to emails and phone calls seven days a week. We do business in accordance with all State and Federal Fair Housing Laws.<br>
